Hello Band Families!

Never sure what to serve for dessert over the holidays or for the guests that just stop by? We have an answer for you:

Munching for Music is offering their annual PIE SALE!

Attached is an order form and instructions to order ‘PIE Certificates’ to redeem at Baker’s Square! You can also choose to donate ‘PIE Certificates’ to the North Royalton Food Bank!

Thank you for supporting the North Royalton Band!

Any questions? Please contact:

Joel Young: 440-230-5562 or joel.s.young@roadrunner.com

Susie Perez: 440-877-1299 or susielbp@juno.com
